Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}物語は終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者は眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}穏やかな日常を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}この地に残して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時の流れは無情に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}人を忘れさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そこに生きた軌跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}錆び付いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それでも君の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉も願いも勇気も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今も確かに私の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}同じ途を選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それだけだったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつの間にかどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}頬を伝う涙の理由をもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}知りたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今更だって
