Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}籠罩了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這是與討伐邪惡的勇者的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}短暫旅途的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}故事結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}平穩的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}生活刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說過的話 你的願望和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也一定能夠找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:01.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}おおげさに泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って欲しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:13.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}鮮明で痛い思い出を抱きしめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}「さよなら」よりずっと大切な言葉で伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:25.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ありふれて でも特別で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:29.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:37.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかった物が どうして溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう一度　生まれ変わろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}また私はここを選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:49.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:54.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あなたとまた巡り合ったら
